{"tid":847761,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【劈價成交】銀禧花園2房業主連劈5口價 終663.8萬沽平市價4%","createTime":"2018-10-04T11:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T07:03:08.000Z","uid":174649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2e481c08b444198340d7e34f3277931582fbf3","tid":847761,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"市道持續疲弱，樓市欠缺利好消息下，業主要沽貨，難逃「一減再減」命運。利嘉閣地產郭建民表示，沙田銀禧花園近日錄大劈價成交，8座高層H室，實用面積約506方呎，建築面積約644方呎，為兩房單位，外望山景。<br />\n<br />\n單位業主2個月前以820萬放售，惟業主因應近期樓市欠缺利好消息支持，加上急需資金週轉，遂於放售期內連續減價五次，最終以663.8萬成交售出，累減逾156萬元，減幅約2成，實用呎價約13,119元，建築呎價則約10,307元。毗連7座高層E室，同屬實用506方呎，上月中成交價690萬元，是次相隔半個月，造價平4%。匯豐銀行網上玄人對該單位估價798萬元，造價低估值134萬元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2012年2月，以約318萬元購入上述單位，是次2轉售賬面可賺約345.8萬元，升幅逾1倍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181004/large/1538626617_1239.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181004%2Flarge%2F1538626617_1239.jpg&h=ada5d750&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4319fd6d3b27d7ac347c3d42997950bae60a5a51","tid":847761,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:54:00.000Z","msg":"邊個接？"},{"pid":"90a3852a35e7738887552e02a32f8c25d0faab3c","tid":847761,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dc3a16ef749cc57da9920b0179d1d733ce3aac4","tid":847761,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"想知邊個夠膽呢d時候接貨咁勁"},{"pid":"4f8bcdeb756d69f4bac3f09ffdbcc3b86ae0f11a","tid":847761,"uid":121387,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4dc3a16ef749cc57da9920b0179d1d733ce3aac4","tid":847761,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"想知邊個夠膽呢d時候接貨咁勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"咁銀行估798萬，劈到去664萬，呢d盤都叫可遇不可求"},{"pid":"3fd9a573ca691ce5469be3e7d8a08662677d1a2c","tid":847761,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:21:52.000Z","msg":"2012年2月，以約318萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec1d17186915ceb298e94555a4e47b0b5e1da69","tid":847761,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:29:11.000Z","msg":"急需資金週轉only"},{"pid":"fd5ad4630d56790f800f3d60fbba78a4279c61bc","tid":847761,"uid":165619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"連劈五口先低市價 4% ，都劈得幾斯文"},{"pid":"bd45d73e15063d9442909bd948e4b9efd2adfe6f","tid":847761,"uid":129340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd5ad4630d56790f800f3d60fbba78a4279c61bc","tid":847761,"uid":165619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"連劈五口先低市價 4% ，都劈得幾斯文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"證明咩？ 證明樓市gogogo 好友又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1022351eb9ae16e566af5bee98063ab35cc8024","tid":847761,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"舊樓，新界唔計"},{"pid":"d77839eef826cd492540e904c1bad85bf1638ee5","tid":847761,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fd9a573ca691ce5469be3e7d8a08662677d1a2c","tid":847761,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:21:52.000Z","msg":"2012年2月，以約318萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:43:16.000Z","msg":"重劈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e745c99659b84c7a07753229cdfecf16a36c125","tid":847761,"uid":75589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfcc9815efecfeb9bbfe7b0cc66c360c14fd35f8","